00:12:23.230 --> 00:12:26.790
These are energy densities.

00:12:26.790 --> 00:12:30.810
And there's a simple
formula for them.

00:12:30.810 --> 00:12:35.460
The electric energy is
equal to the magnitude

00:12:35.460 --> 00:12:38.460
